file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  contact:
    email: analytics.api.support@factset.com
    name: Analytics API Support
    url: https://developer.factset.com/contact
  description: Allow clients to send transactions data to FactSet
  license:
    name: Apache License 2.0
    url: http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt
  title: DSOTM API
  version: "1"
servers:
- url: /
security:
- FactSetApiKey: []
- FactSetOAuth2: []
paths:
  /analytics/dsotm/v1/transactions:
    post:
      description: This endpoint takes the transactions data and pushes them into
        FactSet's systems.
      operationId: sendTransactions
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Transactions'
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Expected response.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "400":
          description: Invalid POST body.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "401":
          description: Missing or invalid authentication.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "403":
          description: User is forbidden with current credentials
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "415":
          description: Missing/Invalid Content-Type header. Header needs to be set
            to application/json.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "429":
          description: Rate limit reached. Retry the requests after waiting the time
            specified in the retry-after header.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirectRequest-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timed out. Retry the request in sometime.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet’s request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet’s request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-FactSet-Api-Request-Key:
              description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                available after successful authentication.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Key to uniquely identify an Analytics API request. Only
                  available after successful authentication.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Push transactions data into FactSet's systems.
      tags:
      - DSOTM
      x-contentType: application/json
      x-accepts: application/json
components:
  schemas:
    ExecutionParameters:
      example:
        symbol: symbol
        settlementvalue: 1.4658129
        amount: 5.637377
        currencyiso: currencyiso
        gross: 6.0274563
        description: description
        transactionid: transactionid
        settlementcurrencyiso: settlementcurrencyiso
        tradetype: tradetype
        transactionleaves: 5.962134
        portfolio: portfolio
        tradedate: tradedate
        foreignexchangerate: 2.302136
        net: 0.8008282
        settlementdate: settlementdate
        status: status
      properties:
        net:
          description: Cash value of the transaction, net of brokerage costs.
          format: float
          type: number
        gross:
          description: Cash value of the transaction, including brokerage costs
          format: float
          type: number
        settlementvalue:
          description: Cash value of the transaction, a value that has been multiplied
            by an applicable FX rates to convert the a transacti
          format: float
          type: number
        settlementdate:
          description: Settlement date in YYYYMMDD format
          type: string
        settlementcurrencyiso:
          description: Currency code for Settlement Value
          type: string
        portfolio:
          description: 'Path of the portfolio (Ex: Client:/folder1/testing.ofdb)'
          type: string
        transactionid:
          description: Unique id for the transaction
          type: string
        symbol:
          description: Symbol corresponding to the traded instrument.
          type: string
        description:
          description: Description
          type: string
        tradetype:
          description: "Trade type could be any of the following values BL, BC, SL,\
            \ SS.\r\nwhich stands for Buy Long, Buy to cover, Sell Long and Sell Short\
            \ respectively."
          type: string
        status:
          description: "Status could be any of the following value: ACCT or CNCL.\r\
            \nwhich stands for Accounted and Cancelled respectively."
          type: string
        tradedate:
          description: Transaction date which is in the format YYYYMMDD
          type: string
        transactionleaves:
          description: Shares that have been ordered and not executed
          format: float
          type: number
        amount:
          description: Quantity of the instrument traded.
          format: float
          type: number
        currencyiso:
          description: The currency code of cash valued fields, Net Amount and Gross
            Amount.
          type: string
        foreignexchangerate:
          description: FX rate that can be picked up by PA, multiplied with the cash
            valued fields, Net, Gross, to allow PA to show transactions in reporting
            currency.
          format: float
          type: number
      required:
      - amount
      - currencyiso
      - gross
      - net
      - portfolio
      - settlementdate
      - settlementvalue
      - status
      - symbol
      - tradedate
      - tradetype
      - transactionid
      type: object
    PlacementParameters:
      example:
        symbol: symbol
        tradetype: tradetype
        transactionleaves: 7.0614014
        amount: 9.301444
        currencyiso: currencyiso
        portfolio: portfolio
        tradedate: tradedate
        foreignexchangerate: 3.6160767
        description: description
        transactionid: transactionid
        settlementcurrencyiso: settlementcurrencyiso
        status: status
      properties:

          type: string
        portfolio:

          type: string
        transactionid:
          description: Unique id for the transaction
          type: string
        symbol:
          description: Symbol corresponding to the traded instrument.
          type: string
        description:
          description: Description
          type: string
        tradetype:
          description: "Trade type could be any of the following values BL, BC, SL,\
            \ SS.\r\nwhich stands for Buy Long, Buy to cover, Sell Long and Sell Short\
            \ respectively."
          type: string
        status:
          description: "Status could be any of the following value: ACCT or CNCL.\r\
            \nwhich stands for Accounted and Cancelled respectively."
          type: string
        tradedate:
          description: Transaction date which is in the format YYYYMMDD
          type: string
        transactionleaves:
          description: Shares that have been ordered and not executed
          format: float
          type: number
        amount:
          description: Quantity of the instrument traded.
          format: float
          type: number
        currencyiso:
          description: The currency code of cash valued fields, Net Amount and Gross
            Amount.
          type: string
        foreignexchangerate:
          description: FX rate that can be picked up by PA, multiplied with the cash
            valued fields, Net, Gross, to allow PA to show transactions in reporting
            currency.
          format: float
          type: number
      required:
      - amount
      - currencyiso
      - portfolio
      - status
      - symbol
      - tradedate
      - tradetype
      - transactionid
      type: object
    OrderParameters:
      example:
        symbol: symbol
        tradetype: tradetype
        transactionleaves: 2.027123
        amount: 4.145608
        currencyiso: currencyiso
        portfolio: portfolio
        tradedate: tradedate
        foreignexchangerate: 7.386282
        description: description
        transactionid: transactionid
        status: status
      properties:
        portfolio:
          description: 'Path of the portfolio (Ex: Client:/folder1/testing.ofdb)'
          type: string
        transactionid:
          description: Unique id for the transaction
          type: string
        symbol:
          description: Symbol corresponding to the traded instrument.
          type: string
        description:
          description: Description
          type: string
        tradetype:
          description: "Trade type could be any of the following values BL, BC, SL,\
            \ SS.\r\nwhich stands for Buy Long, Buy to cover, Sell Long and Sell Short\
            \ respectively."
          type: string
        status:
          description: "Status could be any of the following value: ACCT or CNCL.\r\

          type: string
        tradedate:
          description: Transaction date which is in the format YYYYMMDD
          type: string
        transactionleaves:
          description: Shares that have been ordered and not executed
          format: float
          type: number
        amount:
          description: Quantity of the instrument traded.
          format: float

        currencyiso:

          type: string
        foreignexchangerate:
          description: FX rate that can be picked up by PA, multiplied with the cash

          format: float
          type: number
      required:

      - currencyiso
      - portfolio
      - status
      - symbol
      - tradedate
      - tradetype
      - transactionid
      type: object
    Transactions:
      example:
        executions:
        - symbol: symbol
          settlementvalue: 1.4658129
          amount: 5.637377
          currencyiso: currencyiso
          gross: 6.0274563
          description: description
          transactionid: transactionid
          settlementcurrencyiso: settlementcurrencyiso
          tradetype: tradetype
          transactionleaves: 5.962134
          portfolio: portfolio
          tradedate: tradedate
          foreignexchangerate: 2.302136
          net: 0.8008282
          settlementdate: settlementdate
          status: status
        - symbol: symbol

          amount: 5.637377

          description: description
          transactionid: transactionid
          settlementcurrencyiso: settlementcurrencyiso

          status: status
        placements:
        - symbol: symbol
          tradetype: tradetype

          amount: 9.301444

          description: description
          transactionid: transactionid

        - symbol: symbol

          transactionleaves: 2.027123
          amount: 4.145608
          currencyiso: currencyiso
          portfolio: portfolio
          tradedate: tradedate
          foreignexchangerate: 7.386282
          description: description
          transactionid: transactionid
          status: status
        - symbol: symbol
          tradetype: tradetype
          transactionleaves: 2.027123
          amount: 4.145608
          currencyiso: currencyiso
          portfolio: portfolio
          tradedate: tradedate
          foreignexchangerate: 7.386282
          description: description
          transactionid: transactionid
          status: status
      properties:
        executions:
          description: List of executions
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExecutionParameters'
          type: array
        placements:
          description: List of placements
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlacementParameters'
          type: array
        orders:
          description: List of orders
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/OrderParameters'
          type: array
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    FactSetOAuth2:
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          scopes: {}
          tokenUrl: https://auth.factset.com/as/token.oauth2
      type: oauth2
    FactSetApiKey:
      scheme: basic
